{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/fixed-local-file-path-issue-in-react-library","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"June"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4d65e914-a7c5-5eb3-bb08-f2a7d7684ef1","excerpt":"시작하기 전 잠깐!!! 참고!!! 라이브러리를 만들 때, webpack으로 제작 시 아래와 같이 설정과  설정을 하였습니다.  은 library를 , ,  등으로 사용할 수 있고, 는 해당 library를 build…","html":"<h1 id=\"시작하기-전-잠깐-참고\" style=\"position:relative;\">시작하기 전 잠깐!!! 참고!!!<a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0-%EC%A0%84-%EC%9E%A0%EA%B9%90-%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"시작하기 전 잠깐 참고 permalink\" class=\"autolink-headers-- after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p>라이브러리를 만들 때, webpack으로 제작 시 아래와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">libraryTarget</code>설정과 <code class=\"language-text\">externals</code> 설정을 하였습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f2844b9bb746909bc8f18a34bdaeb9e7/31198/webpack-config.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.666666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAhklEQVQI1xXMSw6DIAAAUc+hTTT+UgRElIoSf7F10fsfaGp3k7eYqChLEjvz8AdJuJCDZzi/tNN690i3venChpk33N99oK4qbPPkdIbVKnwrcc6RZilRXpTE/Uwy7sThg3rN2P3CLCfqngqpkE1DL2qOXiGqkiLPCUYyasGkG5ZOobUmyzJ+w+U+cfX1VW4AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"webpack-config\"\n        title=\"webpack-config\"\n        src=\"/static/f2844b9bb746909bc8f18a34bdaeb9e7/e85cb/webpack-config.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f2844b9bb746909bc8f18a34bdaeb9e7/070ae/webpack-config.png 120w,\n/static/f2844b9bb746909bc8f18a34bdaeb9e7/8ff5a/webpack-config.png 240w,\n/static/f2844b9bb746909bc8f18a34bdaeb9e7/e85cb/webpack-config.png 480w,\n/static/f2844b9bb746909bc8f18a34bdaeb9e7/31198/webpack-config.png 694w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">libraryTarget</code>은 library를 <code class=\"language-text\">umd</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">commonjs</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">esm</code> 등으로 사용할 수 있고, <code class=\"language-text\">externals</code>는 해당 library를 build할 때\n포함하지 않는 옵션입니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>어느 정도 규모가 있는 프로젝트를 하다보면 범용적인 모듈이 생기게 되고, 그 부분은 따로 library화 하게 됩니다.</p>\n<p>React.js, Next.js에서 React 라이브러리를 넣는다면 어떻게 될까요? 사실 큰 문제는 없습니다.\nReact.js 라이브러리는 <code class=\"language-text\">Material-UI</code>나 <code class=\"language-text\">Ant Design</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">React bootstrap</code> 등 이미 알려진게 많습니다.\n이러한 라이브러리, 프레임워크를 사용할 때 큰 문제가 생기는 경우는 거의 없었구요.</p>\n<p>라이브러리를 프로젝트와 함께 만들다 보면 라이브러리를 만들다, 프로젝트를 하다, 하는 스위칭이 생기게 됩니다. 라이브러리가 수정되게 되면 아래와 같이 번거로운 과정을 지속적으로 거쳐야만 합니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>라이브러리를 수정한다.</li>\n<li>package.json 버전을 올린다.</li>\n<li>publish</li>\n<li>프로젝트에서 버전을 올려 다시 설치한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>이 과정을 줄이기 위해 npm package를 file path로 관리할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/cecac/awesome-library.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"awesome-library\"\n        title=\"awesome-library\"\n        src=\"/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/e85cb/awesome-library.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/070ae/awesome-library.png 120w,\n/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/8ff5a/awesome-library.png 240w,\n/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/e85cb/awesome-library.png 480w,\n/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/37523/awesome-library.png 720w,\n/static/e54cdbc5ce6d4796ac8da897d27b78c8/cecac/awesome-library.png 728w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>file path library는 <code class=\"language-text\">npm install</code> 명령어로 설치하게 되면 file path가 node_modules 내에서 symbolic link 연결이 되게 됩니다.\ncreate react app으로 설치한 프로젝트에서 바로 실행해볼까요?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/18f13c39fdebd49b8c499297eb49304d/7131f/create-react-app-example.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create-react-app-example\"\n        title=\"create-react-app-example\"\n        src=\"/static/18f13c39fdebd49b8c499297eb49304d/e85cb/create-react-app-example.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/18f13c39fdebd49b8c499297eb49304d/070ae/create-react-app-example.png 120w,\n/static/18f13c39fdebd49b8c499297eb49304d/8ff5a/create-react-app-example.png 240w,\n/static/18f13c39fdebd49b8c499297eb49304d/e85cb/create-react-app-example.png 480w,\n/static/18f13c39fdebd49b8c499297eb49304d/7131f/create-react-app-example.png 710w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>vscode에서 에러가 발생하지 않습니다. 바로 <code class=\"language-text\">npm start</code> 실행 후 브라우저에서 확인해보겠습니다.\n그런데...?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/3c492/invalid-hooks.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"invalid-hooks\"\n        title=\"invalid-hooks\"\n        src=\"/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/e85cb/invalid-hooks.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/070ae/invalid-hooks.png 120w,\n/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/8ff5a/invalid-hooks.png 240w,\n/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/e85cb/invalid-hooks.png 480w,\n/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/37523/invalid-hooks.png 720w,\n/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/d9199/invalid-hooks.png 960w,\n/static/4f0ce93d237ea4a1ec2c6c9ebf4f4a64/3c492/invalid-hooks.png 1300w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>올바르지 않은 hook의 호출. FC의 내부에서만 사용할 수 있고, 아래와 같은 이유로 문제가 발생합니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ol>\n<li>react와 렌더러의 버전 미스매치</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>hooks의 룰을 따르지 않고 있을 수 있음</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>React 앱이 여러개일 수 있음</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>라이브러리와 프로젝트에서 1, 2번의 룰은 어기지 않았습니다. 의심이 가는건 3번입니다.\n우선 <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/link/invalid-hook-call\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">에러 문구 내의 링크</a>를 따라가봅시다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/warnings/invalid-hook-call-warning.html#duplicate-react\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Duplicate React</a> 이슈가 3번에 해당하는 것으로 보입니다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm ls react</code> 명령어를 실행해봅시다. 문제가 있다면 Error가 발생합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/47218/npm-ls-react.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"npm-ls-react\"\n        title=\"npm-ls-react\"\n        src=\"/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/e85cb/npm-ls-react.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/070ae/npm-ls-react.png 120w,\n/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/8ff5a/npm-ls-react.png 240w,\n/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/e85cb/npm-ls-react.png 480w,\n/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/37523/npm-ls-react.png 720w,\n/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/d9199/npm-ls-react.png 960w,\n/static/6a8c1352bace5482b91d6e114add8aef/47218/npm-ls-react.png 1344w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>라이브러리 내부에서도 react가 있는 중복되는 라이브러리가 1개만 설치되어야 하는데 잘 되네요!</p>\n<p>물론 이는 <code class=\"language-text\">awesome-library</code>에서 <code class=\"language-text\">peerDependencies</code> 설정 해놨기 때문입니다. 이는 내가 만든 모듈이 사용하는 특정 library가 다른 모듈과 함께 사용할 수 있다는 뜻입니다. 또한, <code class=\"language-text\">peerDependencies</code>에 들어가는 라이브러리는 <code class=\"language-text\">devDependencies</code>에 들어가면 <code class=\"language-text\">npm ls ***</code>에서 warning이 날 수 있으므로 <code class=\"language-text\">dependencies</code>에 넣어줘야 합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d45d504c907af8576ed0e2e7c08da93/ff42b/peer-dependencies.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.83333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"peer-dependencies\"\n        title=\"peer-dependencies\"\n        src=\"/static/1d45d504c907af8576ed0e2e7c08da93/e85cb/peer-dependencies.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d45d504c907af8576ed0e2e7c08da93/070ae/peer-dependencies.png 120w,\n/static/1d45d504c907af8576ed0e2e7c08da93/8ff5a/peer-dependencies.png 240w,\n/static/1d45d504c907af8576ed0e2e7c08da93/e85cb/peer-dependencies.png 480w,\n/static/1d45d504c907af8576ed0e2e7c08da93/ff42b/peer-dependencies.png 484w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이번엔 문서에서 체크해보라는 아래 코드를 실행해봅시다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Add this in node_modules/react-dom/index.js</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>React1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Add this in your component file</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'react-dom'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>React2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>React1 <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>React2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">true</code>로 정상적으로 잘 나옵니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/277c6/compare-react-instance1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"compare-react-instance1\"\n        title=\"compare-react-instance1\"\n        src=\"/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/e85cb/compare-react-instance1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/070ae/compare-react-instance1.png 120w,\n/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/8ff5a/compare-react-instance1.png 240w,\n/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/e85cb/compare-react-instance1.png 480w,\n/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/37523/compare-react-instance1.png 720w,\n/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/d9199/compare-react-instance1.png 960w,\n/static/4a49b41475d03b45cc695e77d3e85b5d/277c6/compare-react-instance1.png 2522w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/3126c/compare-react-instance2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.666666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAc0lEQVQI1yWOXQ7CMAyDd5nlt23abiAYD+P+lzJRefgk27GlbLMHvveN99FxNsMwQjFFqRWzaHpGJD1xd4QrpvPKm0n22ro9o+A1A1tvDZ/rwmMOHKMjikNFwSIwIRjv0MSYwMypael/TpDsKu25y2ei4gc0ijyhw16AlAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"compare-react-instance2\"\n        title=\"compare-react-instance2\"\n        src=\"/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/e85cb/compare-react-instance2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/070ae/compare-react-instance2.png 120w,\n/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/8ff5a/compare-react-instance2.png 240w,\n/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/e85cb/compare-react-instance2.png 480w,\n/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/37523/compare-react-instance2.png 720w,\n/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/d9199/compare-react-instance2.png 960w,\n/static/25769a26da66e10c18ceab9551bd5a57/3126c/compare-react-instance2.png 1876w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>문서에 추가로 있는 <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/react/issues/13991#issuecomment-435587809\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">링크</a>도 확인해봅니다.</p>\n<p>문서에 있는 해결방법 중 alias를 추가해보겠습니다.</p>\n<p>alias는 node<em>modules를 가리키는 일반적인 방식 대신, 특정 name의 path를 직접 넣어주는 방식입니다.\nalias로 해결하라는 것은 우선순위가 node</em>modules보다 alias가 높다는걸 뜻합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"># webpack config.resolve.alias\nalias: {\n  react: path.resolve(&#39;./node_modules/react&#39;)\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>TADA! 잘 나오게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 480px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/2c5fd/done.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 98.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"done\"\n        title=\"done\"\n        src=\"/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/e85cb/done.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/070ae/done.png 120w,\n/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/8ff5a/done.png 240w,\n/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/e85cb/done.png 480w,\n/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/37523/done.png 720w,\n/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/d9199/done.png 960w,\n/static/2cf8c7aa281f5950bd1fa657081537ec/2c5fd/done.png 1006w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이로써 React.js 프로젝트에서 React 라이브러리를 사용하는 부분이 잘 동작하게 되었습니다.</p>\n<p>하지만!!!<br>\nNext.js에서는 어떨까요?</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// next.config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">webpack</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">config<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n    config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>alias<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'node_modules'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>동일하게 webpack 설정해 보겠습니다.</p>\n<p>설정한 뒤에도 처음에 보여드렸던 <code class=\"language-text\">invalid hooks</code> 관련 에러가 발생하기도 합니다.\n이럴 땐 <a href=\"https://github.com/martpie/next-transpile-modules\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">next-transpile-modules</a> 라이브러리를 사용하시면 됩니다.</p>\n<p>next.js에서 이런 이슈가 지속되는 경우가 다수 존재하는지, <a href=\"https://github.com/martpie/next-transpile-modules#i-have-trouble-with-duplicated-dependencies-or-the-invalid-hook-call-error-in-react\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">해결책</a>에 대해 나와있고, 이 방법으로 해결했습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> withTM <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'next-transpile-modules'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'aweesome-library'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">withTM</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">webpack</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">config<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>   <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isServer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>     config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>externals <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>externals<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>alias<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>__dirname<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'node_modules'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위에서 \"<code class=\"language-text\">externals</code>는 해당 library를 build할 때 포함하지 않는 옵션입니다.\" 라고 설명을 적어놨는데,\nSSR 시점에는 react 라이브러리가 중복으로 참조되어 발생하는 이슈가 아닐까 추측해봅니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Next.js, React.js 프로젝트 내에서 React.js 라이브러리를 file path로 사용하기 위한 삽질 내용을 정리해 보았습니다.</p>\n<p>위 이슈는 file path로 library를 개발할 때 발생하는 이슈이기 떄문에 npm version 으로 표기를 한다면 <code class=\"language-text\">withTM</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">config.externals</code> 옵션 없이도 잘 동작하게 됩니다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"React library local file path 이슈 해결","date":"March 13, 2021","tags":["next.js","react","library"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/fixed-local-file-path-issue-in-react-library","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/kill-node-prcess"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Kill node process"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["1576648375","764694655"]}